    - "array-flatten README — https://www.npmjs.com/package/array-flatten"
    - "Test vectors verified with array-flatten via Node.js 22.22.1 on Ubuntu 26.04 / Docker, 2026-04-24"
  not_derived_from:
    - "array-flatten source"
  notes:
    - "array-flatten is an npm package. Install: npm install array-flatten"
    - "Flattens nested arrays into a single flat array."
